| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0358 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: acd135e0-cc96-5a3b-92c1-ac7d3523d367"
